Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I'm alright now. I'm much better after a short rest. Sorry for the hassle.

Name: Putra
Phrase: That's all well and good, but you sure you're okay now? Your face looks pale. Your hair is completely white too.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I am born with a white face and hair.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: But don't worry. I'm ready to open the Gate. Now if I can replicate it successfully, I can create an exit on the Hinayashiki side.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Replicate? The exit?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: It means I've recovered enough to use the technique as planned. Look, we're running out of time. Let's get on with it.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Stop, stop. Yuuzen, did you hear what Yoshino said earlier?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: What's it? Ya're getting involved so much.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Not getting involved. Yoshino's just saying that we should have a proper talk before we jump into Hinayashiki.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yuuzen, you're getting ahead of yourself. This isn't the Resistance. This is Shashou's unit. The Special Steel Squad. You can't just go ahead with this or that.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I am not one of ya.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: But you are a collaborator. We're on the same team. You can't just do whatever you want.
Yoshino and Yakutsk have a good point. I don't have any problem with the strategy Yuuzen has set up, but surely there's a bit of an explanation missing, don't you think?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: We didn't expect a lot of monsters or that Yuuzen would be cursed. I don't think it's right to say 'just do as you're told'.

Name: Putra
Phrase: We should all work together to reduce dangers as much as possible. We are all partners fighting together.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I explained earlier what we are going to do.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: We want to hear more details. Yoshino wants you to convince me that Yuuzen can do it properly.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: It's not good to mince words.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Can you really do it? Would you fail like you did with the steel dolls?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino wants to believe in Yuuzen, That's why I want you to reassure everyone.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: You're a good person, Yuuzen. I know you travelled the world with Ricardo and Mary.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: But you are not like Ricardo and Mary. You know what I mean.

Yuuzen let the steel doll run amok in Nishiki. Even though you did not intend it to attack people or towns, you were dealing with uncontrollable forces and almost released dangerous monsters outside as a result.
At that time... Nene would have acted on her own initiative. You caused that situation not for the purposes of the Resistance, but in order to fulfil your personal objectives, Yuuzen.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I know that even if ya didn't tell me. I'm sorry for what happened.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Wait, what about the steel doll?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: It's a terrible ancient mechanical part. A steel doll that spits out Phantom Mist.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Such a dangerous thing!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Yuuzen broke a number of mountain barriers to generate Phantom Mist to power the ancient machine parts back at Iris Cloud. They called her the 'Kekkai Yaburi'.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: It's unbelievable. Mountain barriers are not so easily broken even by sorceresses...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Miss Yuuzen is a woman who travelled the world with Lady Ricardo. She's a sorceress with powers rivalling Mary's. So you can see how powerful she is, can't you?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yuuzen is about to use another dangerous art again. If we leave Yuuzen alone, people will get worried.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: So talk to us properly. Tell everyone what Yuuzen is going to do.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Heh, ya've become more dependable than you were with Nana...

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: ...I understand. I'm also a person to watch out for in yer eyes. It doesn't make sense to ask me to do whatcha say with my cards in my hand.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: What I'm trying to do is apply Gates and sorceries. It uses a tremendous amount of magic power. If I make a mistake in procedure or response, I will die.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: You're going to die...!?

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Could you be more specific?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: First, I'm going to recreate the Gate magic Miyako jumped straight into. This reproduction is a dangerous thing. If I fail, I will never be able to use sorcery ever again.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: And after that?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I'll use the forbidden art of breaking barriers. With this, it will trigger the enemy's traps once more.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Then, taking advantage of this momentary gap... I will read the remaining arts within the torii, which is the medium of the Gate.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: In order to read the lost art, you have to remember the state of the art when it is in effect. Without that, you will end up with a random art.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Don't worry. I already completed the necessary steps to reproduce it when I saved Yoshino that time.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Eh...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: So Yuuzen was planning to help Miyako from the very beginning?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: No, not at all. I was just interested in Hinayashiki.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: As long as I can recreate the Gate, all that's left is to trace the source of the magic and connect the Gates, and if we can fix the location of the exit, we can follow the same path as Miyako.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Even the master of Hinayashiki wouldn't be able to stop this. Only Ricardo and I can use the combination of both Gate and magic.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Yuuzen is really a great sorceress, she's not just a doll master, right?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Have you seen me now? My power is so great that even Shimoamazu of Ooe has recognised me.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Shimoamazu the First, yes? Shimoamazu's mother.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Isn't that a generational thing? Yuuzen seems to be quite old.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Hush ya! Don't be silly! I'm much younger than Shimoamazu the First! I'm younger than Mary.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Oh, you're really mad.

Name: Putra
Phrase: You do care a little bit.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Bah... This is why I don't like to hang out with kids these days...

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: So, what do you think? I told ya my side of the story. I risk my life. If I make a mistake, I'm the first one to die.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I brought ya all here because the odds are stacked against us. I have no intention of throwing away my life. I still have a lot of work to do.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: What are the odds of success?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Half if I'm alone, sevenths if you all come with me.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: I see, got it.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: I believe you, Yuuzen.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yakky-tan.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: I'm relieved to hear the current win rate. I think it's quite a realistic figure. Fifty per cent improving to seventy per cent, so we should all go together. Yuuzen must have thought so.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: It would have been better not to go. Ya might end up with a result that ya regret. Make sure you understand that.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: It's better than regret later, saying 'I should have gone'. We all feel that way.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: And while you're at it, I hope you find what you're looking for, Miss Yuuzen.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: That's good, Yuuzen. Everyone believes in Yuuzen.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino wanted to talk to you for a long time. I was hoping we could meet again.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Thank you, Yuuzen. Thank you for trying your best to help

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Yoshino, remember this.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Don't try to get help from something stronger than ya. Don't think ya're lucky to get help from me.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: In the future, ya'll have to face many obstacles that ya'll have to overcome on your own. Ya shouldn't assume that ya'll get help from me or Mary. Don't say 'help me' as soon as yer friends disappear.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Ya're a sorceress, and ya must take on the curses of those ya care about with the intention of receiving them yerself.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Receiving curses from the people I love...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Miyako is not a 'substitute'. You don't have to get sick or be cursed.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I don't get diseases. I only receive curses.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Why? Why would Miyako do that?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Because it's something only I can do. I receive curses from people. To make people like dolls more...

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Curses are people's emotions. Strong emotions can overcome curses. Ya should have more faith in your feelings for others. Yer precious friend performed miracles that were impossible with sorcery.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino's precious friend...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yes...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino will do her best.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Yep, good luck.
Yuuzen put her hand on Yoshino's head and stroked her big ears a little harder. As a fellow sorceress, as a Nishikese, and as someone who has a friend, this is her advice.
Yoshino's "do her best" words showed a resolve that had never been seen before.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Now then, let's do something spectacular. Is everyone ready?

Name: Putra
Phrase: Ready when you are!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: I won't let them interfere your incantation. You can be rest assured of that.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: As soon as I start the incantation, the Gate will open. As soon as we see Hinayashiki' behind the torii, jump in without hesitation.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: There might be a lot of monsters like before, but pay no heed to them. While I'm holding my ground, everyone will pass through the gate. That's all you need to think about. Don't worry about the guys behind you.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Okay then, let's go...
Yuuzen chanted a curse at the black torii gate. She spoke quite fast, so I can't hear what she is saying at all.
However, I could sense firsthand how powerful the technique she used was, even without understanding the content of the curse.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Do not come near, do not be touched. Do not light up the coma, but go on with the fragrance of the flowers.
The air chatters and trembles. Two great forces collide, distorting the space. Soon, between the pillars of the black torii, a Gate we saw the other that appeared.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Everyone must keep a close eye on the Gate. When ya see Hinayashiki, rush in.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: The enemy is stronger than I thought. The monsters are boiling over too...

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: What are we going to do, Yuuzen? Should we engage and buy some time?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: No, ya can't touch them. I'll take care of them. Ya just concentrate on the Gate and that's it.
Yuuzen took out paper dolls from her pocket and throws it into the air. The paper dolls split into dozens of pieces and flew around the Gate.
They were shikigami created by Yuuzen. They stuck to the approaching monsters and exploded along with them. The shattered shikigami became fragments of magical power and were sucked into the Gate.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: I see it! Hinayashiki!

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Here we go, guys. Queensway, you go with Paddington. Following that it's me, Versailles, Vivienne and Putra, in that order.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Hold my hand, Miss Paddington. Don't let go of my hand, please.

Name: Paddington
Phrase: Aww! Please pick me up, Queensway~!

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: It looks like they all managed to get into the Gate.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Yeah, it seems to have gone well. I'm going to follow ya.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Yoshino, once you get inside Hinayashiki, keep your ears and tail up at all times. If I can't make it, ya'll be the one to lead everyone along.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yes, Yoshino will do my best.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Now, go!
At the same time as Yuuzen's signal, Yoshino jumped into the Gate. I followed Yoshino and submitted myself to the universe connected by Yuuzen.
